tik.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aDiscourse analysisvCongresses. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aAntos, Gerd, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAntos, Gerd, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBeaugrande, Robert de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFix, Ulla, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHartung, Wolfdietrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHornung, Antonie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJakobs, Eva-Maria, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLinke, Angelika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMengel, Swetlana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNussbaumer, Markus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPogner, Karl-Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPortmann-Tselikas, Paul R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPüschel, Ulrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSauer, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTietz, Heike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTietz, Heike, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWiktorowicz, Józef, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aŻmudzki, Jerzy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 1990 - 1999z9783110636895oZDB-23-DLS0 cprintz978348431188640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/97831109408